rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0002
rows.name:
There are plenty of preparations to
make, but first off I should probably
check in with Gramps.

rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0003
rows.name:
If I just took off on a some random ship
without telling him, I'm sure he'd give
me hell later when I came back!

rows.label: fev01_100_155_msg0004
rows.name:
I'd better head down the stairs and
back to Goldmund Return Port.
